Û ailek din heye, jêra dibêjin Mala Ehîko.
 
And there is another family, they call them Mala Ehîko.

595
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,000
Mala Ehîko.
 
Mala Ehîko.

596
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,000
