649
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,000
Ji xwendinê hez dikirin.
 
They loved education.

650
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,000
Wek Kurdaxî.
 
Like Kurds.

651
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,000
Erê.
 
Yes.

